Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.03,0:00:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「花映难波津 隆冬且暂隐」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.03,0:00:05.74,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なにわずに　さくやこのはな　ふゆごもり
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.75,0:00:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「初春又将至 再绽此花矣」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.75,0:00:10.21,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いまをはるべと　さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.63,0:00:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚的节目看了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 看了看了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.49,0:00:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.42,0:00:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生里边有模特绫濑千岁的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.82,0:00:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 我是她的粉丝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那会是超可爱的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.75,0:00:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的? 我们去看看吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.45,0:00:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个班?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.14,0:00:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2班
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.89,0:00:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过据说每天午休时都在休息厅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.94,0:00:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.55,0:00:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑…千早?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.17,0:00:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}かるた（歌留多，骨牌）：用有画的牌来进行的一种竞技游戏，\N竞技歌留多使用小仓百人一首进行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.17,0:00:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竞技歌留多部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.01,0:00:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.23,0:00:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.46,0:01:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二 三 四 !
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.51,0:01:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那是什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.48,0:01:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运动服?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.64,0:01:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 那腰带怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.12,0:01:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑同学!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.85,0:01:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又穿成那种样子…这么不注重仪表!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.27,0:01:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是是老师说这种时候不能穿裙子的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要穿运动服的话 就从上到下都只穿运动服!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.25,0:01:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有你那传单也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.67,0:01:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要贴的话只能贴一张
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能在这里脱!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.70,0:01:31.98,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}你口口声声说要搞竞技歌留多部 上古文课却又一直在睡觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.79,0:01:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 听说她虽然很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.51,0:01:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要一活动一开口 形象就全毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.13,0:01:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以被叫做「白搭美女」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:53.06,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(559,180)\blur11\fad(984,1013)}再绽此花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.71,0:02:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人来啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.45,0:02:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.66,0:03:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「歌留多」什么的 就放弃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.39,0:03:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还是一起玩田径吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.56,0:03:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短跑都进市比赛了 太可惜了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多是…「祸福皆因强出头」那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}原文是「犬も歩けば棒にあたる」，\N出现在古典版的竞技歌留多中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.03,0:03:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说田径部应该叫「邂逅系」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邂逅系?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.82,0:03:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.29,0:03:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该去参加活动了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.44,0:03:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然前辈又要生气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再见啦 小千
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.92,0:03:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:31.66,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}那个前辈啊 可真够恐怖的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊… 有同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来都决定一定要在高中找到同伴…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.54,0:03:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百分之百投入歌留多的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 绫濑就是女王了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}女王（クイーン），指在全国歌留多比赛中，授予\N参加女性组比赛并获得日本第一名的人的称号
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.54,0:04:05.59,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「谁为我知己 未语可知心…」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.54,0:04:05.59,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}たれをかも　しるひとにせむ　たかさごの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正觉得歌留多很快乐是在…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为你总这样「大」字躺着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.33,0:04:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才会被人说成是「白搭美女」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:17.42,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「高砂松虽寿 不及故人情」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:17.42,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}まつもむかしの　ともならなくに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.74,0:04:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太吃惊了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一居然在同一个高中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你一定直升进名校的高中部了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单程要一个半小时才能到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要接着读3年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说刚才那下很痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是千早你考上都立的好高中 让我很意外…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.33,0:04:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长高了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们根本没差多少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小看我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.15,0:04:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还会再长的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.03,0:04:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像也还会再长…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用再长啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:04:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一太一太一 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早 你不怎么受欢迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在? 在车站啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 还没来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 你在分倍河原车站等吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挂咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一 有女朋友吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.93,0:06:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点受打击了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为被告白了我才和她交往
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.78,0:06:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是那么的喜欢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新也找到了比歌留多更重要的事吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.09,0:06:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和新…有联系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年连贺年卡也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.71,0:06:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新…好像去年也没参加全国大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中学在田径部 也没参加过近江神宫的全国大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}最高级别的全国大赛基本都在近江神宫举行，\N因此也被称为竞技歌留多的圣地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加田径部 不也很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.31,0:06:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 高中会做些其他事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多终究只是兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么? 太一不玩歌留多了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得聚在同一所高中的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.84,0:07:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我中学也是以足球部为主的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能永远玩歌留多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.33,0:07:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「谁为我知己 未语可知心」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.33,0:07:09.41,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,たれをかも　しるひとにせむ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这首和歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说以前的朋友都已经没有了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.93,0:07:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续玩下去的话就能再见面的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对要再见面啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.76,0:07:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年前 在东京
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时的我还未曾找到热衷的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐 你姐姐的选美比赛如何了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.63,0:07:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 虽然闯进了最后一轮…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.31,0:07:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 明天的报纸会刊登姐姐的照片哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.56,0:07:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:07:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早的姐姐很漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 太一也这么想?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和千早不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.83,0:08:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 你就只有运动能赶得上我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有身高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 想打架吗 千早
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.42,0:08:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.41,0:08:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个转校生根本不说话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像也没有朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.06,0:08:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要和那家伙扯上关系比较好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说那家伙把虫当零食吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.80,0:08:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 真的假的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2班有人看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袜子上还有洞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.99,0:08:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们班不需要他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 小千
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.82,0:08:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们把绵谷的福井方言记下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过最近他都不说话了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:08:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不能写新的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:08:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是很小气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.36,0:09:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 那次啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是绵谷的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会跟为了嘲笑他而记笔记的人说话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也…不是想那么做的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.19,0:09:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是吗? 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.31,0:09:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.41,0:09:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你忘记拿路线表啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这个的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.73,0:09:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说记住了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.03,0:09:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天才刚开始做啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.38,0:09:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可有200多家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别送错了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2丁目5区
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤原先生和他对面的5家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大泽 藤宫 山本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.64,0:09:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内山先生退订了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.39,0:09:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,横田公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.71,0:10:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,101 103 203 204
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.84,0:10:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一家 绫濑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.67,0:10:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.20,0:10:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.99,0:10:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐上报纸了哦 快醒醒!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.56,0:10:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 还有照片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正还是落选了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能入选最后15人也很厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以把这个照片给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.77,0:10:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你便啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:11:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这个得大奖的人身材确实更好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别总这么说话不经大脑啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千 我看新闻啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.55,0:11:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你姐姐好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.03,0:11:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 好厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.93,0:11:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好厉害 真的登了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你姐姐好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 明明是姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早却还是像个男孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 大家坐好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.05,0:11:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}百人一首：收集一百位歌人各一首的和歌集，\N一般指最出名的「小仓百人一首」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.05,0:11:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸位 百人一首的贴纸集齐没有?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百首都记住了的话 就来参加测试哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:36.52,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}不可能的啦 你记住多少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:38.33,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}才记住10首 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.99,0:11:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记住的人就可以参加下个月的歌留多比赛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.93,0:11:39.94,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}15个~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:41.28,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}这也没差多少吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早 你记住多少了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.53,0:11:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多才到一半吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了行了 学习比不过你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真岛同学 你已经完全记住了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.43,0:11:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是什么都擅长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 安静
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实不只是真岛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:12:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们班还有一个人 也记住了全部一百首哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.00,0:12:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绵谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:07.50,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.23,0:12:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天放学以后 绵谷同学来参加测试
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口气背出了一百首哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:15.09,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}好厉害~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.27,0:12:16.60,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}真的是一口气背下来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家鼓掌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.05,0:12:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下个月的歌留多大赛 你也会出场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…会的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.35,0:12:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.78,0:12:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送报纸的!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.51,0:12:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绵谷同学早上送报纸了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然送报纸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学生是不允许打工的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.83,0:12:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…绵谷同学 是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有叫我帮忙的时候…才去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为家里太穷了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 他一直都穿同一条裤子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 太一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.34,0:12:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绵谷同学很了不起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:12:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能送报纸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 大家安静
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人也要加油把一百首都背下来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绵谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.15,0:13:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见咯 真岛同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.88,0:13:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…那个…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.95,0:13:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.27,0:13:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊 把你唯一的行头弄湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天要穿的衣服没了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆问妈妈借裙子穿…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.93,0:14:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到你会做这么过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 你干嘛总是帮他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要这样 说不定明天起也会被孤立的哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.67,0:14:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会不管你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.93,0:14:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.78,0:14:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说随便你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.10,0:14:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候就算哭我也不管你的哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.45,0:14:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我记住!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.92,0:14:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好破啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不 对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这个人就是说话不经大脑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上也是因为这个挨了姐姐一脚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.69,0:14:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…我说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…可以说话哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会记笔记的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.76,0:15:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么早上…要等报纸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说话了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐参加了选美大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想早点看到那个报导
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.46,0:15:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.47,0:15:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面的这个人就是我姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.39,0:15:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮吧 厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.03,0:15:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的梦想 就是有一天姐姐能成为日本第一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.92,0:15:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种是不能称之为梦想的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.42,0:15:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是自己的事情 就不算是梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以把梦想寄托在别人身上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.81,0:15:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然你姐姐就太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那绵谷同学有什么梦想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.41,0:15:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,属于你自己的!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 这不就是百人一首吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.76,0:16:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑同学你会这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说会不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.22,0:16:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们学校每年都会举办歌留多大赛的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.13,0:16:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 今天老师不也说…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.33,0:16:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}我…我们来比吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以是可以 但是没有人来读啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.07,0:16:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有磁带啊 磁带
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.44,0:16:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么有干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…怎么弄来着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把25张牌分成三组排好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.30,0:16:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到上句读出来 就要拿掉下句对应的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.30,0:16:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}上句（上の句），指短歌的前半五·七·五三句，\N下句（下の句）则指剩下的第四、第五句
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在才只背下来50个左右
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 就是个歌留多比赛而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.67,0:16:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种眼神 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以开始了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.33,0:17:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「秋来红叶散…」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.33,0:17:14.64,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あらしふく…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.29,0:17:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.66,0:17:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「天工织做锦 还缀龙田川」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.66,0:17:29.18,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,662)}たつたのかはの　にしきなりけり
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又扎到门里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「今时辛酸泪 老来润心田」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:42.86,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ながらへば　またこのごろや　しのばれむ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.91,0:17:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.95,0:17:54.51,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「世间千般愁 欲解竟无方」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.95,0:17:54.51,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}よのなかよ　みちこそなけれ　おもひいる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.26,0:17:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多…以前是这样玩的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.81,0:17:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.33,0:17:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.02,0:18:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.86,0:18:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不甘心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.32,0:18:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要抢到一张
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那张牌的上句我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.51,0:18:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「激流戏浅水 岩前两纷飞」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.51,0:18:22.61,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(660,658)}せをはやみ　いはにせかるる　たきがはの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要抢到那一张
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有那一张
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.78,0:18:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想抢到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.91,0:18:38.72,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「激…」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.91,0:18:38.72,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}せ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.58,0:18:51.86,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「…流戏浅水 岩前两纷飞」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.58,0:18:51.86,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}…をはやみ　いはにせかるる　たきがはの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 抢到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.95,0:18:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从绵谷同学那里抢到一张了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢指教
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这算什么啊 强得过头了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.44,0:19:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是绫瀬同学也抢到了一张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有这一张啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.66,0:19:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.57,0:19:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我很开心!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在福井的时候 经常和朋友们一起玩歌留多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 东京却没什么人玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.38,0:19:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都是一个人玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人? 听着磁带?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.78,0:19:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多在其他国家都没什么人玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为确实比较难
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.85,0:19:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这也就意味着…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.64,0:19:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在日本取得第一的话 就是世界第一了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界…第一?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加歌留多比赛 成为名人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}名人：与女王相对，是授予男性的\N代表歌留多日本第一名称号
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.35,0:19:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「千早」…是个好名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 这是属于你的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张牌的上句 是以「神代有蓬莱」开头的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:16.77,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(740,658)}ちはやぶる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为听到「ちはや」就要抢这张牌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:18.86,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(600,658)}千早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}ちはやぶる，日文汉字可以写成「千早振」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.09,0:20:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这张牌就是「ちはや」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.77,0:20:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的眼中就是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.11,0:20:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.64,0:20:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新 这是你的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.49,0:20:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 女朋友吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.27,0:20:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小女朋友 吃地瓜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「神代有蓬莱 今看龙田川」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:50.14,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ちはやぶる　かみよもきかず　たつたがは
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.21,0:20:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙真的好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.66,0:21:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「奇景未曾见 江揽红叶衫」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.66,0:21:06.76,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,からくれなゐに　みづくくるとは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次和新玩歌留多的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.86,0:21:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所知道的不是歌留多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是新的热情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.98,0:22:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.33,0:22:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是「千早HOO！」的解说员上田真理绘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.11,0:22:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从漫画大赛开始获得各种大奖的超人气漫画《花牌情缘》
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.68,0:22:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.82,0:22:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饰演主人公绫濑千早的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.99,0:22:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朝气蓬勃的女高中生濑户麻沙美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.13,0:22:58.13,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}她直率的富有透明感的演技
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.53,0:23:01.53,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}使她这次被选为绫濑千早的饰演者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.03,0:23:05.03,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}并演唱了ED「そしていま」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:22:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样是高中生的我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.20,0:23:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很是憧憬和羡慕千早对于歌留多的那种拼命的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.00,0:23:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把自己想象成千早 来演绎这个角色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.67,0:23:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 竞技歌留多虽然是不太被熟知的一个竞技项目
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.77,0:23:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是它的趣味性和热血 我会通过表演传达给大家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.73,0:23:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻沙美 加油哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
